Text: 'After a breakup from a Relationship which was Latter Diagnosed as abusive Relation
  Ship. I ran 1200 km in Berlin crying each Step missing my ex girlfriend. Then i
  Complete Berlin Marathon 3:41 hours. But subtel abuse was still going on. Then in
  Dezember i teavelled to thailand before i went to my Parents in Nepal.

  The path of my self healing and seeing so many loopholes in my ex behaviour which
  i never realisied during my Relationship.


  This is Story of a rise and Fall of a Love.'
